Title: Georg Fischer Primofit galvanised male adaptor (BSP/Steel) (NBR Seal) 1/2"
Description: This Georg Fischer Primofit 1/2 x 1/2" adapter is made of malleable cast iron and incorporates BSP tapered x compression connections. Durable and highly resistant to mechanical stress and temperatures, this fitting is safe for use in a wide range of settings and offers universal, standardised thread jointing technology combined with pre-assembled Primofit compression joints. With full end load capability, this fitting ensures fast and reliable connection of steel, PE, lead and butt-weld steel pipes.
